lead_paragraph: Hungary's Katinka Hosszu gave up her bid for a record-equalling five solo women's Olympic swimming medals on Tuesday as some of the sport's top names also wrestled with Rio's late night schedules.

headline.print_headline: Swimming: Hosszu Pulls Out as Adrian Squeaks Through
